WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.250 --> 00:00:07.500
This blade has a dark past.

2
00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.800
It has shed much innocent blood.

3
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.450
You're a fool for traveling alone,
so completely unprepared.

4
00:00:18.750 --> 00:00:21.800
You're lucky your blood's still flowing.

5
00:00:22.250 --> 00:00:23.300
Thank you.

6
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:26.000
So...

7
00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:30.800
What brings you to
the land of the gatekeepers?

8
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.500
I'm searching for someone.

9
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.200
Someone very dear?
A kindred spirit?

10
00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:42.000
A dragon.

11
00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:48.750
A dangerous quest for a lone hunter.

